","marks":[],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"In this article, we explored how to protect sensitive information in logs when using ReportPortal and REST Assured logger. We covered three cases of sensitive information exposure in logs and how to handle them using ReportPortal's built-in functionality. `ReportPortalRestAssuredLoggingFilter` class has converters and prettifiers configuration which we can use and extend to cover our needs. We also learned how to create custom converters and prettifiers to handle specific cases of sensitive information exposure in logs.","marks":[],"data":{}}]}]}
